WEBVTT

00:08:59.310 --> 00:09:02.235
It's the ability to think critically:

00:09:02.259 --> 00:09:03.978
call out falsehood,

00:09:04.002 --> 00:09:05.429
press for the facts.

00:09:06.802 --> 00:09:10.995
And above all, you must have the courage

00:09:11.019 --> 00:09:13.967
to unflinchingly pursue the truth.

00:09:15.752 --> 00:09:20.790
(Applause)